  "instructions": [
    "Heat the coconut oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the sliced onion and cook for 3 minutes, or until translucent.",
    "Add the sliced mushrooms and cook for an additional 3 minutes, or until they start to brown.",
    "Add the sliced red bell pepper, carrots, and sweet potatoes, and cook for 5 minutes, or until the vegetables start to soften.",
    "Add the curry powder, thyme, garlic powder, salt, and black pepper, and stir to combine.",
    "Add the rice vermicelli and stir to combine with the vegetables and spices.",
    "Cook for an additional 2-3 minutes, or until the vermicelli is lightly toasted.",
    "Taste and adjust the seasoning as needed.",
    "Transfer the stir-fry to a serving dish and serve hot."
